title: Furnished 1 bed + Den & Balcony Available Now! Parking, Gym & More!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Konrad on the Park', 'Vibrant city living with a rare parkside appeal.', 'Just steps from the culture and convenience of Hayes Valley, Konrad on the Park is an intimate boutique apartment building featuring elevated finishes, clean design, and enviable proximity to Jefferson Square Park.', 'Equally a recharging refuge and well-connected nexus, this collection of studios, one- and two-bedroom homes allows residents to enjoy the city as they choose, whether indulging in the surrounding green space or taking in panoramic views from a signature ~6,000-square-foot rooftop terrace.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Resident Ambassador', 'Gym with Personal Training', 'Package Room with Cold Storage', 'HIIT Fitness Center with Weekly Classes', '6,000 Sq.', 'Ft. Rooftop Terrace with Lounge Areas', 'Community Bicycles', 'Outdoor Kitchen & Dining Area', 'BBQ & Fire Pits', 'Pet Friendly', 'Secure & Assigned Parking', 'EV Parking', 'Terraces and Balconies on Select Residences', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!', 'View our availability to find your new home!', 'Rates shown are net effective rents and factor in current special.', 'Contact our leasing office for more details on move-in specials.', 'Terms & conditions apply.']
